---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import NotaryQuiz from '../../components/NotaryQuiz.astro';
import WeeklyNews from '../../components/WeeklyNews.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="基里巴斯公证人 - Tekarei Tautua 女士 | 认证公证服务"
  description="Tekarei Tautua 女士，基里巴斯共和国正式任命的公证人。为国内和国际使用提供法律文件的专业认证和鉴定服务。"
  lang="zh"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">Notary Tautua</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">Tekarei Tautua – 公证人，基里巴斯共和国</Fragment>

  <section class="nt-hero">
    <div class="nt-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="nt-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="nt-hero-content">
      <h1 class="nt-title">公证人</h1>
      <p class="nt-name">Tekarei Tautua 女士</p>
      <p class="nt-lead">以诚信、精确和完全尊重法律标准提供专业公证服务。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">广告位 - Google AdSense</div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>文件认证</h2>
      <p>法律文件的官方认证，包括宣誓书、法定声明、授权委托书和宣誓声明，供基里巴斯境内和境外使用。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>国际鉴定</h2>
      <p>为国际使用进行文件鉴定和合法化。为个人、企业和政府机构提供跨境文件需求的支持。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>见证与证明</h2>
      <p>专业见证签名、宣誓和确认。每项证明均严格遵守适用的法律要求。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>认证副本</h2>
      <p>为法律、移民和行政目的准备和认证原始文件的真实副本。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>商业服务</h2>
      <p>为公司文件、合同、合伙协议和需要官方认证的商业交易提供公证服务。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>保密与诚信</h2>
      <p>每项服务均以严格的保密性、准确性和遵守基里巴斯共和国适用法律要求的方式提供。</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ad-slot">广告位 - Google AdSense</div>

  <NotaryQuiz lang="zh" />

  <div class="ad-slot">广告位 - Google AdSense</div>

  <WeeklyNews lang="zh" />

  <section class="contact-info">
    <h2>联系方式</h2>
    <p><strong>Tekarei Tautua</strong> – 公证人</p>
    <p>贝蒂奥，南塔拉瓦</p>
    <p>邮政信箱 118</p>
    <p>基里巴斯共和国</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">广告位 - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .nt-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: -40px -20px 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .nt-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url('/images/notary.webp');
    background-size: contain;
    background-position: center center;
    background-color: #0a0c12;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }
  .nt-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(10,12,18,.55) 0%,
      rgba(10,12,18,.7) 50%,
      rgba(10,12,18,.85) 100%
    );
  }
  .nt-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    padding: 40px 24px;
  }
  .nt-title {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    letter-spacing: -.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .nt-name {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #d4a853;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
  }
  .nt-lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .nt-title { font-size: 2.4rem; }
    .nt-name { font-size: 1.4rem; }
    .nt-lead { font-size: 1rem; }
  }
  .contact-info {
    background: rgba(212,168,83,.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212,168,83,.12);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .contact-info h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #d4a853;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }
  .contact-info p {
    margin: 6px 0;
    color: rgba(245,230,200,.55);
  }
</style>
